Install global gems:

    rvm @global do gem install gem-browse

Aliases

    rvm alias create ruby-1.9.3 ruby-1.9.3-falcon
    rvm use ruby-1.9.3

Install/upgrade ruby:

    rvm @global do gem list
    rvm get head
    rvm requirements
    rvm install 1.9.3 --patch falcon
    rvm upgrade 1.9.3-p327 1.9.3-p385
    # or
    rvm gemset copy ruby-2.0.0-p247@global ruby-2.0.0-p353@global

SSL Problems?

    curl -L get.rvm.io | bash -s stable

